<span id="freeTextContainer5218156207291895925">What a story !!! The Author, Jon Clinch, stayed the course, never wandered into something meaningless. He kept me interested thru out.<br/>The Story is about a Jewish family - mom, dad, daughter and a 14 year old son, that did ALL they could to stay alive as a FAMILY. The Mother, an artist and the dad a barber make thier mark at Auschwitz. Unfortunately the daughter loses her life the first day. Now, the artist, the barber and the son, must figure out how to survive of what&apos;s left of the family. Ahhh</span>
