<span id="freeTextContainer15377077566741209533">As its survivors slowly leave us, the brutal cost of the Holocaust for millions upon millions of families grows dim even though Shoah projects across the globe scramble to preserve stories of the perished and connect survivors. The Thief of Auschwitz is an intimate, necessary representation of one family’s love and sacrifice in this horrific context. Even if the convergence of events would have been unlikely in the randomness of the larger reality, this compelling tale reminds us to honor such f</span>
  <span id="freeText15377077566741209533" style="display:none">As its survivors slowly leave us, the brutal cost of the Holocaust for millions upon millions of families grows dim even though Shoah projects across the globe scramble to preserve stories of the perished and connect survivors. The Thief of Auschwitz is an intimate, necessary representation of one family’s love and sacrifice in this horrific context. Even if the convergence of events would have been unlikely in the randomness of the larger reality, this compelling tale reminds us to honor such families in an important, transcendent way. </span>
  <a data-text-id="15377077566741209533" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

