<div id="review_579077914" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/579077914" />
    <a title="Cherylann" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2426596-cherylann"><img alt="Cherylann" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1345894915p2/2426596.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/579077914?book_show_action=true">Apr 02, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cherylann" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cherylann" href="/user/show/2426596-cherylann">Cherylann</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2426596-cherylann?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer579077914" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2703418124232312294">Since I teach the Holocaust each year, I felt like I had a pretty good idea of the time period and the atrocities that took place. The Thief of Auschwitz is a brief look at life in Auschwitz - specifically about what happens to one family as they enter the camp. Compelling and gripping, The Thief of Auschwitz is a new look at a horrific time in history.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


