<div id="review_1088318368" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1088318368" />
    <a title="Liz Hobbins" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/27334151-liz-hobbins"><img alt="Liz Hobbins" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1088318368?book_show_action=true">Oct 24, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Liz Hobbins" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Liz Hobbins" href="/user/show/27334151-liz-hobbins">Liz Hobbins</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1088318368" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9109430091060887098">My favorite from Jon Clinch - very different from his other two - he did a wonderful job of conveying the horror of the camp without actually providing any detailed events - I really felt the bond between the members of the Rosen family, manifested in spite of their physical separation. A touching novel, at once sad and triumphant.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


