<div id="review_643062252" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/643062252" />
    <a title="Charlie Newfell" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/10767970-charlie-newfell"><img alt="Charlie Newfell" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1412723684p2/10767970.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/643062252?book_show_action=true">Jun 16, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Charlie Newfell" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Charlie Newfell" href="/user/show/10767970-charlie-newfell">Charlie Newfell</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer643062252" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2428142754208704465">Wonderfully written, and although describes the absolute horrors and suffering of Auschwitz, it&apos;s the little vignettes that will stay with you. These stories humanize it for all of us who can&apos;t fathom what it was like. A must read. </span>
  <span id="freeText2428142754208704465" style="display:none">Wonderfully written, and although describes the absolute horrors and suffering of Auschwitz, it's the little vignettes that will stay with you. These stories humanize it for all of us who can't fathom what it was like. A must read. </span>
  <a data-text-id="2428142754208704465" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


